description: Permutation of natural numbers: rotations of all branches of the rooted plane trees encoded by A014486. (to opposite direction of A057511).
links: Index entries for sequences that are permutations of the natural numbers
maple: # See A057510 for rotateR, A057501 for other procedures.map(CatalanRankGlobal,map(DeepRotateR, A014486));DeepRotateR := n -> pars2binexp(deeprotateR(binexp2pars(n)));deeprotateR := proc(a) if 0 = nops(a) or list <> whattype(a) then (a) else rotateR(map(deeprotateR,a)); fi; end;
